history.content:
Interested in learning about industry job and research opportunities, revamping your resume with advice from recruiters, working on technical projects, or meeting tons of new friends through socials (and free food)? Consider joining Berkeley IEEE!

Fill out our interest form to stay updated!

Our general/committee member applications are out! Apply here

Our first event is a Resume Workshop with Texas Instruments on Wednesday, 9/1 at 5:00pm PDT! RSVP here
history.subject: Join IEEE today!
